{"tid":2324500,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[細龍太的pat pat] 「細龍太」陳偉琪畀老外新歡長揸靚股 當街挑逗手指喪撩裙底","createTime":"2020-12-14T03:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T16:14:45.000Z","uid":121711,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2f204d605edd5da4a57444a8d15f41c17dba864e","tid":2324500,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kJRzT9qS5x4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkJRzT9qS5x4&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725Cq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=5bc79e31\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kJRzT9qS5x4</a><br />\n<br />\n入行7年，擁有36E 倒奶身材的陳偉琪，3年前憑住《愛.回家之開心速遞》演「細龍太」一角，成功入屋。劇中的「細龍太」水性陽花，現實生活中，陳偉琪的感情生活一樣多姿多彩。負面新聞不斷，加上去年因為醉駕，被大台掟入雪櫃足足一年。上星期「細龍太」終於在台慶獲「解凍」。<br />\n<br />\n「量地」一年，事業有返聲氣，日前《壹仔》更發現，「細龍太」原來秘密有新戀情。當日她孖住外籍新歡，齊齊幫襯「閨蜜」髮型師Ryan 剪頭髮。轉完個look 之後，二人到商場附近搵食，沿路老外隻手一直徘徊在「細龍太」的pat pat ，之後更伸手撩她裙底，不知幾鬼馬！"},{"pid":"fb8682d9cbb9ce38f3cd4153fb6800689f275425","tid":2324500,"uid":228894,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/11TMWrc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F11TMWrc.jpg&h=40d0c111&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da7321c40ebcd19186ef0ed2eafa9977a39ccea6","tid":2324500,"uid":20867,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:56:34.000Z","msg":"新香港人：老外<br />\n舊香港人：鬼佬"},{"pid":"f73248af7d00a51eff1ef2d6ff5c24b14047f456","tid":2324500,"uid":16777,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:57:49.000Z","msg":"呢條女肯定係女上騎爆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c5482a403450534f7cfa671794e2a21899befe","tid":2324500,"uid":158411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:04:24.000Z","msg":"褲嚟㗎喎"},{"pid":"d47f1afa76cecc4c1f32278ab9c4129c6509ed4d","tid":2324500,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T0